  "detailed_description": "\"Tech Disorder\" plunges players into a cyberpunk dystopia, blending Turn-based strategy, Roguelike chaos, and Deckbuilding complexity. In this game, you navigate a neon-lit world on the brink of technological collapse, where every decision shapes your journey. Customize your strategy with a dynamic deck of cybernetic enhancements, battle against cyber-enhanced foes and robots in strategic turn-based combat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823630/extras/9234b28cb7fea5842eca157cac0c858d.avif?t=1714256044\" width=589 height=119 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823630/extras/fd890ddf445250154d5de349e083e1ef.poster.avif?t=1714256044\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823630/extras/fd890ddf445250154d5de349e083e1ef.webm?t=1714256044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823630/extras/fd890ddf445250154d5de349e083e1ef.mp4?t=1714256044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823630/extras/6266442661ff8b2bde2303b38c90c8ad.avif?t=1714256044\" width=589 height=119 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823630/extras/93d5a09cb9e0603fcb01814ae804e328.poster.avif?t=1714256044\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823630/extras/93d5a09cb9e0603fcb01814ae804e328.webm?t=1714256044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c